        "\n",
        "**Solution**\n",
        "\n",
        "**Step 1:** $~$ Solve the homogeneous system\n",
        "\n",
        "We begin by solving the homogeneous system:\n",
        "\n",
        "$$\\mathbf{x}' = \\mathbf{A}\\mathbf{x}$$\n",
